Text: FW Interview wEnron Fri Mar pmJeff Per your request I am attaching a list of questions for you for the Friday meeting Nancy Egger Special Assistant to the Secretary for Resources FAX Original Message From mailto Sent Wednesday March PM To Subject Interview wEnron Fri Mar pm Hello Nancy Heres the name and email address of the contact at Enron well be speaking with this Friday who wants to see the questions beforehand If you wouldnt mind forwarding him the set of Marketing questions Id greatly appreciate it Jeff Dasovich Many thanks Michle Michele Yoskovich McKinsey Company California Street Suite San Francisco California Telephone Sacramento Fax Forwarded by Michele YoskovichSFONorthAmericaMCKINSEY on PM Michele Yoskovich To Zander ArkinSFONorthAmericaMCKINSEY Daniel PollerHOUNorthAmericaMCKINSEY PM cc Jacqui CKINSEY Kelly CKINSEY Subject Interview wEnron Fri Mar pm TO Susan Glick Zander Daniel with ccs for fyis to assistants of Mary Nichols Lenny Mendonca and Rob Latoff Phone Interview with Enrons TimeDate Fri Mar pm Location Steve or Deputys office Attendees Steve Larson Zander Arkin andor Daniel Poller and from Enron Jeff Dasovich Head of Regulatory PR Call in Place call to Jeffs office at Additionally Mary Nichols will be informed of the meeting in case she is available to attend Thank you Michele Yoskovich McKinsey Company California Street Suite San Francisco California Telephone Sacramento This message may contain confidential andor privileged information If you are not the addressee or authorized to receive this for the addressee you must not use copy disclose or take any action based on this message or any information herein If you have received this message in error please advise the sender immediately by reply email and delete this message Thank you for your cooperation Marketersdoc
